## Quick Restore Commands

# If only code is broken:
git reset --hard HEAD

# If everything is broken:
rm -rf venv
python3.12 -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
git reset --hard HEAD

# To see all restore points:
git log --oneline
